reviewText: i feel that this should be  a 10 min read rather than a guided tutorial. kinda wasting my time and it's my fault that i was expecting more. this course was more like an excel function tutorial rather than PM template, i think this could be more cool if the course explore more on how to implement the template based on real scenarios. not focusing on formats etc.

I decided while waiting for another esponse the take the quiz anyway and I passed with the minium of 80% and got my certificate. How ever this scares to to take anymore of these types of courses in the future.
